CatDescriptText: David L. Lawrence was Mayor of the City of Pittsburgh 1946-1959, Governor of Pennsylvania 1959-1963, and he died in 1966.
TitMainTitle: Men and women, including speaking man seated at head of table with gavel and hands together, and Pittsburgh Mayor David L. Lawrence holding document in background, in ornate interior with tall windows, gathered in Pittsburgh City Council Chambers at the City County Building
